Write a program code in the ST language for a PLC according to the IEC/EN 61131 standard for a conveyor (Conveyor), where only one phase is active at a time:

Pressing the Start button activates Loading.
After 10 seconds, it switches to Transporting.
After another 10 seconds, it switches to Unloading.
When presence_sensor indicates completion, the sequence returns to Loading.
Pressing the Stop button interrupts the sequence, and the conveyor stops.







